==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: chiropteran
<hw>chiropteran</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>nocturnal mouselike mammal with
forelimbs modified to form membranous wings and anatomical adaptations
for echolocation by which they navigate.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> bat.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

